//		Warning (NTSTATUS)					0x8XXXXXXX (PSC_STATUS_XXX)
//		Information (NTSTATUS)				0x4XXXXXXX (PSC_STATUS_XXX)
//		Success (NTSTATUS)					0x0XXXXXXX (PSC_STATUS_XXX)
